channel.title: [HELP ME] Need help Running a 508 server
channel.description:
Hello,
i'm using UmairScape V4, And when i click Run it shows this: [URL=http://img253.imageshack.us/my.php?image=plaatjedinges8.jpg][IMG]http://img253.imageshack.us/img253/7020/plaatjedinges8.th.jpg[/img][/URL]The text is Dutch,
here is it in english: The System cant find the Path, Press any key to continue
What to do to Run it?
Please help me.
